<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Header file for functions to creating Metal layers and views on SDL windows. </para>
</section>
<section>
<title>Typedef Documentation</title>
<anchor xml:id="__s_d_l__metal_8h_1a0d6413e2d369fbf22f0a2e4ec15bf412"/><section>
    <title>SDL_MetalView</title>
<indexterm><primary>SDL_MetalView</primary><secondary>SDL_metal.h</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>SDL_metal.h</primary><secondary>SDL_MetalView</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>typedef <link linkend="__s_d_l__opengles2__gl2ext_8h_1ae5d8fa23ad07c48bb609509eae494c95">void</link>* <link linkend="__s_d_l__metal_8h_1a0d6413e2d369fbf22f0a2e4ec15bf412">SDL_MetalView</link></computeroutput></para><para>

<para>A handle to a CAMetalLayer-backed NSView (macOS) or UIView (iOS/tvOS). </para>
</para>

<para><note><title>Note</title>

<para>This can be cast directly to an NSView or UIView. </para>
</note>
</para>
</section>
</section>
